| Background      = group_or_band
| Alias           = '''A'''gnetha&lt;br /&gt;'''B'''jörn&lt;br /&gt;'''B'''enny&lt;br /&gt;'''A'''nni-Frid
| Origin          = [[Stockholm]], Sweden
| Genre           = [[Pop rock]], [[disco]], [[europop]], [[synthpop]]
| Years_active    = 1972–1982
| Label           = [[Polar Music|Polar]] (Sweden)&lt;br /&gt;[[Polydor Records|Polydor]]&lt;br /&gt;(Germany/The Netherlands)&lt;br /&gt;[[Atlantic Records|Atlantic]] (United States/Canada)&lt;br /&gt;[[Universal Music Group|Universal]] (USA)&lt;br /&gt;[[Epic Records|Epic]] (UK/Italy)&lt;br /&gt;[[Disques Vogue|Vogue]] (France)&lt;br /&gt;Discomate&lt;br /&gt;[[RCA Records|RCA]] (Australia/South America/Mexico)&lt;br /&gt;[[PolyGram]]&lt;br /&gt;Carnaby&lt;br /&gt;Sunshine (Rhodesia-Zimbabwe)&lt;br /&gt;Ariston/Dig It (Italy)
