* A. J. Ayer, ''[http://www.google.ca/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;cd=4&amp;ved=0CDgQFjAD&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fvif2ne.ru%2Fnvz%2Fforum%2Ffiles%2FPutt%2F%2528090310102202%2529_ayer.pdf&amp;rct=j&amp;q=Language%2C%20Truth%2C%20and%20Logic&amp;ei=YHRlTe2gLYa0lQeLxajwBg&amp;usg=AFQjCNFT93qN6gQWs63l5_CmYQGjuy3gaw&amp;sig2=DYc1-HfC5-2WNClSVl7jww&amp;cad=rja Language, Truth, and Logic]'', ISBN 0-486-20010-8
* George H. Smith, ''[http://www.andrew.cmu.edu/user/jksadegh/A%20Good%20Atheist%20Secularist%20Skeptical%20Book%20Collection/George%20H.%20Smith%20-%20Atheism-%20The%20Case%20Against%20God%20%28v1.1%29.pdf Atheism, the Case Against God]'', ISBN 0-87975-124-X
